# C# mod conventions

- netstandard2.1, nullable enabled
- `internal` default; namespace `MimesisPlayerEnhancement.Features.{Feature}`
- Descriptive names; `_` prefix on private fields
- Brief comments for host-only rules, game quirks, timing constraints only
- Features, config, build, logging, patches: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)
